node.text:
Emblematic and unified aesthetics.
#Reverso
_
Reverso Tribute Small Seconds 
_
The sunray-brushed dial offers a colour palette of rare complexity, ranging from a bright to a dark green depending on the light exposure. Featuring all of the signature design elements of the Reverso Tribute, the hours are marked by applied indexes. Their faceted shape echoes the form of the Dauphine hands and adds visual depth to the dial. 
_

Reverso, a Story of Innovation.
#ReversoStories
_
The Reverso Exhibition Shanghai, China.
_
A Story of Innovation explores how the Reverso embodies Jaeger-LeCoultre’s eternally inventive quest for technical advancement. Beginning with the revolutionary idea of a case that could be flipped over, to the ingenious design by Rene-Alfred Chauvot, patented in 1931, the story traces the introduction of high-watchmaking complications.
_
